        Just like Google's Teachable Machine lets you train AI models without complex coding, 
        modern JavaScript frameworks let you build powerful web applications with elegant simplicity.
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
        <a href="/teachable-machine" 
           class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
          Explore Teachable Machine Concept
        </a>
        <a href="/flask-integration" 
           class="border border-gray-300 text-gray-700 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
          See Flask Integration
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Framework Comparison Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      
