          <li>‚Ä¢ Multi-framework support</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ Exceptional performance</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ Content-focused websites</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- React/Next.js Card -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 border-l-4 border-blue-500">
